"tid":216663,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:24:56.000Z","msg":"如果巴老釘左巴郡起碼會回20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a035d8c8a625233e20a5638c163a9ce156728b2","tid":216663,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果巴老釘左巴郡起碼會回20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申：九up"},{"pid":"1ff54f1db2d8d85be5420b083e8c5524528f54d9","tid":216663,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0267532007506cea926e1819e8e72caf0d173f","tid":216663,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/big5/20170505/mkt104834.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Fbig5%2F20170505%2Fmkt104834.asp&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=4a18c939\" target=\"_blank\">http://cn.wsj.com/big5/20170505/mkt104834.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n巴菲特對IBM失去信心 已拋售所持約三分之一IBM股份<br />\n<br />\n國際商業機器公司的問題越來越多，億萬富豪巴菲特周四稱，因對IBM失去信心，他麾下公司已將所持約三分之一的IBM股份賣出。<br />\nMIKE MURPHY<br />\n2017年 05月 05日 10:47<br />\n<br />\n國際商業機器公司(International Business Machines, IBM, 簡稱IBM)的問題越來越多，億萬富豪巴菲特(Warren Buffett)周四稱，因對IBM失去信心，他麾下公司已將所持約三分之一的IBM股份賣出。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特向CNBC 表示，2016年底伯克希爾哈撒韋公司(Berkshire Hathaway Inc., BRKA)持有約8,100萬股IBM股份，但今年以來已賣出約3,000萬股。<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特告訴CNBC，現在他對IBM的估值與六年前開始買入時已有所不同，他對該公司的估值已經有些下調。<br />\n<br />\n伯克希爾哈撒韋曾經一度是IBM的最大股東，持有後者約130億美元股份。不過，巴菲特向CNBC表示，IBM的表現並沒有像他所預期的那樣，而且該公司遇到了一些非常強勁的競爭對手。巴菲特稱，他已完成出售該股。<br />\n<br />\n周三，穆迪(Moody)將IBM的信用評級從A1下調至Aa3，理由是IBM在嘗試向雲計算公司轉型過程中面臨挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n（本文譯自MarketWatch）"},{"pid":"d35a3d441ed9035e185ef055856f0406dd22a388","tid":216663,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d4e361333a6a6a4f0879837ade8abb31ec8b03","tid":216663,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"與青年人為敵嘅經濟日報集團旗下周刊imoney今期即刻將巴菲特做封面，仲叫人係香港搵類似股票，怕香港人唔知咁。"},{"pid":"b9c73d5d0986dd3e92333bb76d911ca4d3a5f265","tid":216663,"uid":18795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T14:45:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.video.yahoo.com/brklivestream2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.video.yahoo.com%2Fbrklivestream2017&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=22ea3b6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.video.yahoo.com/brklivestream2017</a>"},{"pid":"7a651d0027eab1b3772fc9a5535b1f78daffdfd7","tid":216663,"uid":101751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"業績ok la"},{"pid":"64106e1013689272e19b3f4dc61b1d695dc4f167","tid":216663,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91Ch6c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91Ch6c.png&h=bb3bfcf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdaa0ef51dc4a6a3c639362ff39649ab5c77a32","tid":216663,"uid":101751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91Ch6c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91Ch6c.png&h=bb3bfcf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉"},{"pid":"ac70f060f426eb19abcf818467cf717c19551714","tid":216663,"uid":9328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"開始緊？"},{"pid":"24f676061138e65f366dc76e18f61eee9e4aa5b3","tid":216663,"uid":101751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開始緊？</blockquote><br />\n開始左啦"}]}